---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Taylor Heathcote | Design & Production">
  <div class="split-grid" style="margin-bottom: 2rem; align-items: stretch;">
    <section>
      <p class="eyebrow">Game Design • Media Production • Creative Thinking</p>
      <h2>
        Hi, I’m Taylor, a creative generalist with a thoughtful eye for
        design, structure, and player experience.
      </h2>
      <p class="lead">
        I’m interested in game design, production-minded thinking, clear
        communication, and making ideas feel intentional. I care about
        polish, readability, and the little details that make creative
        work feel considered.
      </p>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a href="/projects" class="button button-primary">View Projects</a>
        <a href="/cv" class="button button-secondary">Read CV</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">Approach</p>
      <h2>Thoughtful ideas, clear structure, and a human touch.</h2>
      <p>
        I like work that feels carefully shaped — not just functional,
        but coherent, readable, and memorable.
      </p>

      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Focus</p>
      <p>Design, presentation, systems, and creative direction.</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <p class="eyebrow"></p>
    <h1>Projects</h1>

    <div class="project-grid">
      <article class="project-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">UI / UX / Addon Design</p>
        <h3>GrandRP: Profiles & Utilities</h3>
        <p>
          A roleplay addon concept for World of Warcraft focused on profile
          presentation, usability, and polished character-facing design.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Narrative / Systems Design</p>
        <h3>The Clouded Shore</h3>
        <p>
          A two-player tabletop campaign concept built around collaborative
          discovery, magical mystery, and strong character involvement.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="project-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Brand / Frontend / Content Design</p>
        <h3>Taylor Portfolio Website</h3>
        <p>
          A custom-coded personal portfolio built to communicate creativity,
          polish, and thoughtful design sensibility.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="split-grid">
    <section class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
      <h2>A creative mindset with a production instinct.</h2>
      <p>
        I enjoy shaping ideas into something legible, intentional, and
        worth engaging with. That includes design thinking, organisation,
        communication, presentation, and keeping an eye on how everything
        fits together.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">What I Bring</p>
      <p><strong>Design awareness:</strong> clarity, tone, structure, and player-facing thinking.</p>
      <p><strong>Communication:</strong> ideas explained clearly and presented with care.</p>
      <p><strong>Polish:</strong> attention to detail in both systems and presentation.</p>
      <p><strong>Creative flexibility:</strong> comfortable across concept, planning, writing, and UI thinking.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>